    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of large European linden growing 20-40 m tall with a trunk up to 1-2 m diameter. It is widely planted in rows as a street tree, famously in Berlin's Unter den Linden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
